org.mortbay.setuid
Class Passwd

java.lang.Object
  org.mortbay.setuid.Passwd

public class Passwd
extends Object

Class is the equivalent java class used for holding values from native c code structure passwd. for more information please see man pages for getpwuid and getpwnam struct passwd { char *pw_name; // user name char *pw_passwd; // user password uid_t pw_uid; // user id gid_t pw_gid; // group id char *pw_gecos; // real name char *pw_dir; // home directory char *pw_shell; // shell program };

Author:
Leopoldo Lee Agdeppa III
